description:
The Federal Penguin Affairs Agency has decided to redeploy Regiment 100 of the Penguin Tangle Air Force (PTAF). Are you ready to protect the Tangle Universe in all three dimensions? We are looking for the most skilled penguins!

You can see your standing in the PTAF on the following page: www.penguintangleforces.com

The collection consists of 179 penguins and 4 bonus cards. No. 178 was part of a giveaway.

Good Luck!
name: Penguin Tangle Air Force
